snippet.title: Wrestling With Emotions: New Kid on The Block - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing Team Lazerbeam's latest game punk creation;
Wishlist  'Wrestling With Emotions - New Kid On the Block' today!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1431250/

Befriend, seduce, enrage and bodyslam musclebound heartthrobs in the next chapter of our cuddly choice-based life/wrestling/dating sim, Wrestling With Emotions!

Wanna keep up with all the latest from Team Lazerbeam? Join us on Discord!
discord.gg/T5P9vbt

Thanks forever to Free Lives, Future Friends and all our other lovely buds who helped us get to this point! Love ya! Appreciate ya!
